          <title>
            <string language="fi">Alatiuhta, kahden alta</string>
            <string language="en">Lower lease, under two</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Senken Sie Miete, unter zwei</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Abaissez le bail, au-dessous de deux</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Abaixe o aluguer, sob dois</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Abbassi il contratto d'affitto, sotto due</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Χαμηλότερη μίσθωση, κάτω από δύο</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Baje el arriendo, bajo dos</string>
          </title>
          <language>fi</language>
          <description>
            <string language="fi">Värivalokuvassa nainen asettelee loimilankoja kahden alatiuhdan puun alta.</string>
            <string language="en">Colour photograph of a woman placing the warp yarns under two pegs of the lower lease.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="fi">luomapuut</string>
            <string language="fi">loimi</string>
            <string language="fi">alatiuhta</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Färben Sie Fotographie einer Frau, welche die 
Warpgarne unter zwei Stöpsel der untereren Miete plaziert.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Colorez la photographie d'une femme plaçant les 
filés de chaîne au-dessous de deux chevilles du bail inférieur.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Colora a fotografia de uma mulher que coloca os 
fios de urdidura sob dois Pegs do aluguer mais baixo.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Colori la fotografia di una donna che dispone i 
filati per ordito sotto due spine del contratto d'affitto più basso.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Φωτογραφία χρώματος μιας γυναίκας που τοποθετεί τα 
νήματα στρεβλώσεων κάτω από δύο γόμφους της χαμηλότερης 
μίσθωσης.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Coloree la fotografía de una mujer que coloca 
los hilados de deformación bajo dos clavijas del arriendo más bajo.</string>
          </description>
